//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/LittleSimz-Glastonbury-Festival-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/LittleSimz-Glastonbury-Festival-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/LittleSimz-Glastonbury-Festival-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/LittleSimz-Glastonbury-Festival-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/LittleSimz-Glastonbury-Festival-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a>谈到了她即将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上</a>的表演，并调侃粉丝们可以期待“身临其境的体验”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年阵容揭晓 – 看看谁在比赛</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-wins-the-2022-mercury-prize-for-sometimes-i-might-be-introvert-3331258">水星奖</a>得主说唱歌手将在今年的音乐节上在标志性的金字塔舞台上表演，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a> 、酷玩乐队 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>将成为该音乐节的主角。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/little-simz-at-glastonbury-2022-review-west-holts-stage-3255499">Simz 成为 2022 年 Wests Holts 舞台的头条新闻</a>， <em>《NME》</em>在四星评价中称该节目展现了“说唱杰作中完美的决定论”。在离开舞台之前，这位 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/little-simz-no-thank-you-review-lyrics-artwork-3365363">《不，谢谢你》</a>艺术家告诉观众：“下次金字塔见！”</p><p>今天早上（3 月 14 日），Simz 在 BBC Radio 6 Music 节目中告诉主持人 Lauren Laverne，她对 Glasto 即将回归感到“兴奋不已”。 “这太棒了，”她补充道（来自<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/171739/Little-Simz-All-roads-are-leading-for-me-to-Glasto-so-I-m-really-taking-time-to-craft-a-show" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>音乐新闻</em></a>）。</p><p> Simz 曾于 2016 年和 2019 年在格拉斯顿伯里演出，他解释道：“我认为我的格拉斯顿伯里之旅非常独特，但事实上，他们一直支持我，并不断带我回来参加更大的舞台，在不同的时间和东西。是的，确实如此，很特别。”</p><p>她补充道：“我记得 [2022 年] 走开时说，‘下次在金字塔上见’，而这确实发生了。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4fRf2liQQ4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 